Dizengoff Nigeria has appointed Mr. Graham John Leslie as its new country manager. He took over from Mr. Antti Ritvonen, who has been the country manager since 2015. He obtained a Bachelor of Science degree in agricultural production and a Master of Business Administration (MBA) in economics and marketing from the University of Stellenbosch, South Africa. Prior to his appointment, according to a statement, Leslie was the sales and commercial director of synergy, covering Europe and the United Kingdom. With this appointment, Leslie will continue to provide strategic leadership and direction for the Nigeria business.